    "content": "<div class=\"note\">\n<p>Work on this is being tracked in <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1453783\" title=\"[meta] Support top-level chrome HTML windows\">bug 1453783</a> and <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1446829\" title=\"[meta] Remove in-content XUL\">bug 1446829</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This page gathers technical solutions to common problems encountered by teams shipping HTML-based interfaces inside Firefox.</p>\n\n<p>Background: </p>\n\n<p>Discussion of how to replace XUL is ongoing within the Platform team. In the meantime, some teams are already experimenting with HTML5-based interfaces.</p>\n\n<p>Problems / solutions:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">accessibility</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">localization</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">caching for working offline / pre-caching for snappy first run</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">visual performance / jank</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">security</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">privacy</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">operations</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">Tooling</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\">\n  <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">Build process</strong></p>\n </li>\n <li dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1d7853c-6405-9d22-1fe8-394f2e42b9bf\">Third-party library use and management</strong></li>\n</ul>",
